<concept id="dimadec" xml:lang="en-US">
   <title id="title__Toc50994959">DIMADEC System Variable</title>
   <conbody>
      <section><title>Dim angle precision</title><p>Specifies the display precision for angular dimensions. Values between -1 and 8 are accepted. If -1 is entered, DIMADEC is initialized with the value of the DIMDEC setting. Values 0 to 8 specify the number of decimal places for angular dimensions, independent of DIMDEC.</p><p>
            <table id="table_r32_ncz_hnb">
               <tgroup cols="2">
                  <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="1*" />
                  <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="3*" />
                  <tbody>
                     <row>
                        <entry conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/type" />
                        <entry><p conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/short" /></entry>
                     </row>
                     <row>
                        <entry conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/saved_in" />
                        <entry><p conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/drawing" /></entry>
                     </row>
                     <row>
                        <entry conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/range" />
                        <entry>
                           <p>-1 to 8</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row>
                        <entry conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/default_value" />
                        <entry><p>0</p></entry>
                     </row>
                     <row>
                        <entry conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/possible_values" />
                        <entry>
                           <p>-1: Use DIMDEC setting</p>
                           <p>0 - 8: Decimal places</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                  </tbody>
               </tgroup>
            </table>
         </p></section>
   </conbody>
